README.TiVo

startncid      - used to start ncid on a TiVo that does not have services

initmodem      - used to signal ncidd to re-initialize the modem
                 will also start ncidd if it is not running

The following scripts are not useful on the TiVo and may be removed:
    ncidsip
    ncidrotate
    ncidtools
    ncid-kpopup
    ncid-mythtv
    ncid-samba
    ncid-speak
